To create similar page.
Open your IDE (mine was VSCode) and create these files.
- Index.html
- script.js
- style.css
- images folder where you will save all your images you will use for the site
- index.php and composer.json

After creating your site according to your liking put this code under the index.php
- <?php include_once("index.html");?>

and this brackets under composer.json {}

Once done upload it to GIThub and go sign in to heroku. 
Once signed in create new app and choose GIThub for deployment method.
Then choose your repo and follow the instruction to finish deploying your app.
